M|requesting-code-review|1. rv {WHAT_WAS_IMPLEMENTED}
M|requesting-code-review|2. Compare against {PLAN_OR_REQUIREMENTS}
M|requesting-code-review|3. Check code quality, architecture, testing
M|requesting-code-review|4. Categorize issues by severity
M|requesting-code-review|5. Assess prd readiness
M|requesting-code-review|{DESCRIPTION}
M|requesting-code-review|{PLAN_REFERENCE}
M|requesting-code-review|**Base:** {BASE_SHA}
M|requesting-code-review|**Head:** {HEAD_SHA}
