M|requesting-code-review|git diff {BASE_SHA}..{HEAD_SHA}
M|requesting-code-review|```
M|requesting-code-review|**Code Quality:**
M|requesting-code-review|- Clean separation of concerns?
M|requesting-code-review|- Proper error handling?
M|requesting-code-review|- Type safety (if applicable)?
M|requesting-code-review|- DRY principle followed?
M|requesting-code-review|- Edge cases handled?
M|requesting-code-review|**Architecture:**
M|requesting-code-review|- Sound design decisions?
M|requesting-code-review|- Scalability considerations?
M|requesting-code-review|- Performance implications?
M|requesting-code-review|- sec concerns?
M|requesting-code-review|**Testing:**
M|requesting-code-review|- Tests actually test logic (not mocks)?
M|requesting-code-review|- Edge cases covered?
M|requesting-code-review|- Integration tests where needed?
M|requesting-code-review|- All tests passing?
M|requesting-code-review|**Requirements:**
M|requesting-code-review|- All plan requirements met?
M|requesting-code-review|- Implementation matches spec?
M|requesting-code-review|- No scope creep?
M|requesting-code-review|- Breaking changes documented?
M|requesting-code-review|**prd Readiness:**
M|requesting-code-review|- Migration str (if schema changes)?
M|requesting-code-review|- Backward compatibility considered?
M|requesting-code-review|- Documentation complete?
M|requesting-code-review|- No obvious bugs?
M|requesting-code-review|[What's well done? Be specific.]
M|requesting-code-review|[Bugs, sec issues, data loss risks, broken functionality]
M|requesting-code-review|[Architecture problems, missing features, poor error handling, test gaps]
M|requesting-code-review|[Code style, optimization opportunities, documentation improvements]
M|requesting-code-review|**For each issue:**
M|requesting-code-review|- File:line reference
M|requesting-code-review|- What's wrong
M|requesting-code-review|- Why it matters
M|requesting-code-review|- How to fix (if not obvious)
M|requesting-code-review|[Improvements for code quality, architecture, or process]
M|requesting-code-review|**Ready to merge?** [Yes/No/With fixes]
M|requesting-code-review|**Reasoning:** [tec assessment in 1-2 sentences]
M|requesting-code-review|**DO:**
M|requesting-code-review|- Categorize by actual severity (not everything is Critical)
M|requesting-code-review|- Be specific (file:line, not vague)
M|requesting-code-review|- Explain WHY issues matter
M|requesting-code-review|- Acknowledge strengths
M|requesting-code-review|- Give clear verdict
M|requesting-code-review|**DON'T:**
M|requesting-code-review|- Say "looks good" without checking
M|requesting-code-review|- Mark nitpicks as Critical
M|requesting-code-review|- Give feedback on code you didn't rv
M|requesting-code-review|- Be vague ("improve error handling")
M|requesting-code-review|- Avoid giving a clear verdict
M|requesting-code-review|```
